</div>
<div class="jp-InputArea jp-Cell-inputArea"><div class="jp-InputPrompt jp-InputArea-prompt">
</div><div class="jp-RenderedHTMLCommon jp-RenderedMarkdown jp-MarkdownOutput " data-mime-type="text/markdown">
<h2 id="4th-order-Runge-Kutta-method-adapted-to-the-model"><strong>4th order Runge-Kutta method adapted to the model</strong><a class="anchor-link" href="#4th-order-Runge-Kutta-method-adapted-to-the-model">&#182;</a></h2><p>Algorithm adapted to remove oscillations around $C$ and used to formulate the scenarios.</p>

</div>
</div>
</div>
</div><div class="jp-Cell jp-CodeCell jp-Notebook-cell jp-mod-noOutputs  ">
<div class="jp-Cell-inputWrapper">
<div class="jp-Collapser jp-InputCollapser jp-Cell-inputCollapser">
</div>
<div class="jp-InputArea jp-Cell-inputArea">
<div class="jp-InputPrompt jp-InputArea-prompt">In&nbsp;[&nbsp;]:</div>
<div class="jp-CodeMirrorEditor jp-Editor jp-InputArea-editor" data-type="inline">
     <div class="CodeMirror cm-s-jupyter">
<div class=" highlight hl-ipython3"><pre><span></span><span class="k">def</span> <span class="nf">RK</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">Tn</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">Mn</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">Cn</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">h</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">tmax</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">tanalise</span><span class="p">):</span> 
  <span class="n">npassos</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="n">tmax</span><span class="o">/</span><span class="n">h</span>
  <span class="n">cont</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="mi">1</span>
  <span class="c1">#We create empty lists to receive the results of the iterations</span>
  <span class="n">tempo</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="mi">0</span>
  <span class="n">t</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="p">[]</span>
  <span class="n">Tn1</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="p">[]</span>
  <span class="n">Mn1</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="p">[]</span>
  <span class="n">Cn1</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="p">[]</span>
  <span class="c1">#Lists that will receive the results of the iterations</span>
  <span class="n">t</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">append</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">tempo</span><span class="p">)</span>
  <span class="n">Tn1</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">append</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">Tn</span><span class="p">)</span>

      <span class="n">Cn</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="n">Cn</span><span class="o">+</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="mf">1.0</span><span class="o">/</span><span class="mf">6.0</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="o">*</span><span class="n">h</span><span class="o">*</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">m1</span><span class="o">+</span><span class="mi">2</span><span class="o">*</span><span class="n">m2</span><span class="o">+</span><span class="mi">2</span><span class="o">*</span><span class="n">m3</span><span class="o">+</span><span class="n">m4</span><span class="p">)</span>

    <span class="c1">#The updated values are stored in the vectors</span>
    <span class="n">Tn1</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">append</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">Tn</span><span class="p">)</span>
    <span class="n">Mn1</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">append</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">Mn</span><span class="p">)</span>
    <span class="n">Cn1</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">append</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">Cn</span><span class="p">)</span>
    <span class="n">t</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">append</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">tempo</span><span class="p">)</span>

<span class="n">S1tumor1</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">S1macr1</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">S1cart1</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">S1tempo1</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="n">RK</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">C1</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">],</span><span class="n">C1</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">],</span><span class="n">C1</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">2</span><span class="p">],</span><span class="n">h</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">tmax</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="mi">20</span><span class="p">)</span>

<h2 id="Sensitivity-analysis"><strong>Sensitivity analysis</strong><a class="anchor-link" href="#Sensitivity-analysis">&#182;</a></h2><p>We performe a sensitivity analysis using the elemtary effects (EE) and the adapted algorithm.</p>

<div class=" highlight hl-ipython3"><pre><span></span><span class="kn">import</span> <span class="nn">numpy</span> <span class="k">as</span> <span class="nn">np</span>
<span class="kn">import</span> <span class="nn">pandas</span> <span class="k">as</span> <span class="nn">pd</span>
<span class="kn">import</span> <span class="nn">matplotlib.pyplot</span> <span class="k">as</span> <span class="nn">plt</span>
<span class="kn">from</span> <span class="nn">SALib.sample.morris</span> <span class="kn">import</span> <span class="n">sample</span> <span class="k">as</span> <span class="n">ee_sample</span>

<span class="c1">##### Makes graphics font look like LaTeX font</span>
<span class="kn">import</span> <span class="nn">matplotlib</span>
<span class="n">matplotlib</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">rcParams</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="s1">'mathtext.fontset'</span><span class="p">]</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="s1">'cm'</span>
<span class="n">matplotlib</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">rcParams</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="s1">'font.family'</span><span class="p">]</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="s1">'STIXGeneral'</span>

        <span class="k">if</span> <span class="p">(</span><span class="n">i</span> <span class="o">&gt;</span> <span class="n">tanalise</span><span class="o">/</span><span class="n">h</span><span class="p">):</span>
            <span class="n">aux</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="n">Cn</span><span class="o">+</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="mf">1.0</span><span class="o">/</span><span class="mf">6.0</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="o">*</span><span class="n">h</span><span class="o">*</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">m1</span><span class="o">+</span><span class="mi">2</span><span class="o">*</span><span class="n">m2</span><span class="o">+</span><span class="mi">2</span><span class="o">*</span><span class="n">m3</span><span class="o">+</span><span class="n">m4</span><span class="p">)</span> 
            <span class="k">if</span> <span class="p">(</span><span class="n">Cn1</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="n">i</span><span class="o">-</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">]</span><span class="o">&lt;=</span><span class="n">aux</span><span class="p">):</span>
                <span class="n">Cn</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="n">Cn1</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="n">i</span><span class="o">-</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">]</span>        
                <span class="n">cont</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="mi">0</span>
            <span class="k">elif</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">cont</span><span class="o">==</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">):</span>
                <span class="n">Cn</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="n">Cn</span><span class="o">+</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="mf">1.0</span><span class="o">/</span><span class="mf">6.0</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="o">*</span><span class="n">h</span><span class="o">*</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">m1</span><span class="o">+</span><span class="mi">2</span><span class="o">*</span><span class="n">m2</span><span class="o">+</span><span class="mi">2</span><span class="o">*</span><span class="n">m3</span><span class="o">+</span><span class="n">m4</span><span class="p">)</span>
        <span class="k">else</span><span class="p">:</span>
            <span class="n">Cn</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="n">Cn</span><span class="o">+</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="mf">1.0</span><span class="o">/</span><span class="mf">6.0</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="o">*</span><span class="n">h</span><span class="o">*</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">m1</span><span class="o">+</span><span class="mi">2</span><span class="o">*</span><span class="n">m2</span><span class="o">+</span><span class="mi">2</span><span class="o">*</span><span class="n">m3</span><span class="o">+</span><span class="n">m4</span><span class="p">)</span>


        <span class="n">Tn1</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">append</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">Tn</span><span class="p">)</span>
        <span class="n">Mn1</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">append</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">Mn</span><span class="p">)</span>
        <span class="n">Cn1</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">append</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">Cn</span><span class="p">)</span>
        <span class="n">t</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">append</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">tempo</span><span class="p">)</span>    

    <span class="k">return</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="n">Tn1</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">Mn1</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">Cn1</span><span class="p">]</span>


<span class="c1">##### WRAPPER: ALLOWS THE MODEL TO ROLL AGAIN WITH NEW PARAMETER SETS ##### </span>
<span class="k">def</span> <span class="nf">modelo_wrapper</span><span class="p">(</span>
    <span class="n">y0</span><span class="p">,</span>
    <span class="n">t_eval</span><span class="p">,</span>
    <span class="n">alpha1</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">beta1</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">alpha2</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">alpha3</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">K1</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">K2</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">mu1</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">kappa2</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">kappa3</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">theta3</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">gamma3</span><span class="p">):</span>

    <span class="c1">##### Adapted 4th order Runge-Kutta method</span>
    <span class="n">solution_prob</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">RK</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">y0</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">t_eval</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">alpha1</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">beta1</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">alpha2</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">alpha3</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">K1</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">K2</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">mu1</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">kappa2</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">kappa3</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">theta3</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">gamma3</span><span class="p">)</span>
     
    <span class="k">return</span> <span class="n">solution_prob</span>

 
<span class="c1">########### MODEL PARAMETERS ######################</span>

<span class="n">alpha1</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="mf">0.69</span> <span class="p">;</span><span class="n">beta1</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="mf">2.3e-10</span>
<span class="n">alpha2</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="mf">1e-7</span><span class="p">;</span><span class="n">alpha3</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="mf">5e-8</span> 
<span class="n">K1</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="mf">1e9</span> <span class="p">;</span><span class="n">K2</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="mf">1e9</span>  
<span class="n">mu1</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="mf">1e-7</span> 
<span class="n">kappa2</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="mf">0.34</span> <span class="p">;</span><span class="n">kappa3</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="mf">0.13</span>
<span class="n">theta3</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="mf">1e-10</span> <span class="c1">#Enter too small a number, method does not accept zero</span>
<span class="n">gamma3</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="mf">4e-8</span> 

<span class="c1">########### INITIAL CONDITIONS ######################</span>
<span class="n">TUMOR_ic</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="mf">2e6</span>
<span class="n">MAC_ic</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="mf">1e6</span>
<span class="n">CAR_ic</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="mf">1e5</span>
<span class="n">y0_modelo</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">TUMOR_ic</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">MAC_ic</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">CAR_ic</span>

<span class="c1">### TIME ###</span>
<span class="n">tmax</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="mi">80</span>     
<span class="n">h</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="mf">0.01</span> 
<span class="n">times</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">np</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">arange</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">tmax</span><span class="o">+</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">h</span><span class="p">)</span>

<span class="c1">##### THE DECLARED PARAMETERS ARE ENTERED AS THE AVERAGE SENSITIVITY PARAMETERS ##### </span>

<span class="n">mean_values_params</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="p">[</span><span class="n">alpha1</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">beta1</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">alpha2</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">alpha3</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">K1</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">K2</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">mu1</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">kappa2</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">kappa3</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">theta3</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">gamma3</span><span class="p">]</span>
<span class="n">factors_names</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="p">[</span>
    <span class="sa">r</span><span class="s1">'$\alpha_1$'</span><span class="p">,</span> 
    <span class="sa">r</span><span class="s1">'$\beta_1$'</span><span class="p">,</span> 
    <span class="sa">r</span><span class="s1">'$\alpha_2$'</span><span class="p">,</span> 
    <span class="sa">r</span><span class="s1">'$\alpha_3$'</span><span class="p">,</span> 
    <span class="sa">r</span><span class="s1">'$K_1$'</span><span class="p">,</span> 
    <span class="sa">r</span><span class="s1">'$K_2$'</span><span class="p">,</span> 
    <span class="sa">r</span><span class="s1">'$\mu_1$'</span><span class="p">,</span> 
    <span class="sa">r</span><span class="s1">'$\kappa_2$'</span><span class="p">,</span> 
    <span class="sa">r</span><span class="s1">'$\kappa_3$'</span><span class="p">,</span> 
    <span class="sa">r</span><span class="s1">'$\theta_3$'</span><span class="p">,</span> 
    <span class="sa">r</span><span class="s1">'$\gamma_3$'</span>
<span class="p">]</span>

<span class="c1">##### Problem definition</span>
<span class="n">seed</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="mi">1234</span>
<span class="n">params_perturbations</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="mf">0.25</span> <span class="c1">#####  Parameter variation 25%</span>

<span class="n">problem_info</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="p">{</span>
    <span class="s1">'num_vars'</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="nb">len</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">mean_values_params</span><span class="p">),</span>
    <span class="s1">'names'</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="n">factors_names</span><span class="p">,</span>
    <span class="s1">'bounds'</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="p">[[</span><span class="n">param</span> <span class="o">-</span> <span class="n">params_perturbations</span> <span class="o">*</span> <span class="n">param</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">param</span> <span class="o">+</span> <span class="n">params_perturbations</span> <span class="o">*</span> <span class="n">param</span><span class="p">]</span> <span class="k">for</span> <span class="n">param</span> <span class="ow">in</span> <span class="n">mean_values_params</span><span class="p">]</span>
<span class="p">}</span>

<span class="c1">#####  Parameters of the Elem. Effects</span>
<span class="n">grid_level</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="mi">4</span> <span class="c1">##### p - levels</span>
<span class="n">num_of_trajectories</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="mi">40</span> <span class="c1">##### r-trajectories</span>
<span class="n">parameter_values</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">ee_sample</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">problem_info</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">grid_level</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">num_of_trajectories</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">local_optimization</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="kc">False</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">seed</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="n">seed</span><span class="p">)</span> <span class="c1">##### Gera vários "sets" de parâmetros</span>

<span class="c1">##### Defining output arrays</span>

<span class="n">num_of_experimental_points</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="nb">len</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">times</span><span class="p">)</span> <span class="c1">#Number of observations/experimental points analyzed</span>
<span class="n">num_of_realizations</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">parameter_values</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">shape</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">]</span> <span class="c1">#Number of samples (number of parameter sets generated by Elem. Effects)</span>

<span class="c1">#####  We will analyze sensitivity for 1-Tumor, 2-Macrophage, 3-CART</span>
<span class="n">qoi_sensitivity_outputs1</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">np</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">zeros</span><span class="p">([</span><span class="n">num_of_realizations</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">num_of_experimental_points</span><span class="p">])</span>
<span class="n">qoi_sensitivity_outputs2</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">np</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">zeros</span><span class="p">([</span><span class="n">num_of_realizations</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">num_of_experimental_points</span><span class="p">])</span>
<span class="n">qoi_sensitivity_outputs3</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">np</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">zeros</span><span class="p">([</span><span class="n">num_of_realizations</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">num_of_experimental_points</span><span class="p">])</span>

<span class="c1">##### Tests and saves result in all previously generated parameter sets</span>
<span class="k">for</span> <span class="n">realization_index</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">parameters_realization</span> <span class="ow">in</span> <span class="nb">enumerate</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">parameter_values</span><span class="p">):</span>
    
    <span class="n">realization_model</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">modelo_wrapper</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">y0_modelo</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">times</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="o">*</span><span class="n">parameters_realization</span><span class="p">)</span>

    <span class="n">tumor_sol</span><span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">realization_model</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">]</span>
    <span class="n">mac_sol</span><span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">realization_model</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">]</span>
    <span class="n">car_sol</span><span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">realization_model</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">2</span><span class="p">]</span>
    
    <span class="n">qoi_sensitivity_outputs1</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="n">realization_index</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="p">:]</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">tumor_sol</span> <span class="c1">#Amount of interest - tumor</span>
    <span class="n">qoi_sensitivity_outputs2</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="n">realization_index</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="p">:]</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">mac_sol</span> <span class="c1">#Amount of interest - TAM</span>
    <span class="n">qoi_sensitivity_outputs3</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="n">realization_index</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="p">:]</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">car_sol</span> <span class="c1">#Amount of interest - CART</span>

<span class="c1">##### Collecting and processing the results</span>
<span class="kn">from</span> <span class="nn">SALib.analyze.morris</span> <span class="kn">import</span> <span class="n">analyze</span> <span class="k">as</span> <span class="n">ee_analyze</span>

<span class="n">Si_list1</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="nb">list</span><span class="p">()</span>
<span class="n">df_Si1</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">pd</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">DataFrame</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">columns</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="s1">'Time (days)'</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="o">*</span><span class="n">problem_info</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="s1">'names'</span><span class="p">]])</span> <span class="c1">#names columns</span>
<span class="n">df_Si1</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="s1">'Time (days)'</span><span class="p">]</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">times</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">round</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">)</span> <span class="c1">#fills column  'Time (days)'</span>

<span class="n">Si_list2</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="nb">list</span><span class="p">()</span>
<span class="n">df_Si2</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">pd</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">DataFrame</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">columns</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="s1">'Time (days)'</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="o">*</span><span class="n">problem_info</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="s1">'names'</span><span class="p">]])</span> <span class="c1">#nomeia colunas</span>
<span class="n">df_Si2</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="s1">'Time (days)'</span><span class="p">]</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">times</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">round</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">)</span> <span class="c1">#fills column  'Time (days)'</span>

<span class="n">Si_list3</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="nb">list</span><span class="p">()</span>
<span class="n">df_Si3</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">pd</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">DataFrame</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">columns</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="s1">'Time (days)'</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="o">*</span><span class="n">problem_info</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="s1">'names'</span><span class="p">]])</span> <span class="c1">#nomeia colunas</span>
<span class="n">df_Si3</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="s1">'Time (days)'</span><span class="p">]</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">times</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">round</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">)</span> <span class="c1">#fills column  'Time (days)'</span>

<span class="c1">##### Run the EE</span>
<span class="k">for</span> <span class="n">experimental_point</span> <span class="ow">in</span> <span class="nb">range</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">num_of_experimental_points</span><span class="p">):</span><span class="c1">#number of observations/experimental points collected </span>
    <span class="n">Si1</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">ee_analyze</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">problem_info</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">parameter_values</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">qoi_sensitivity_outputs1</span><span class="p">[:,</span> <span class="n">experimental_point</span><span class="p">],</span> <span class="n">conf_level</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="mf">0.95</span><span class="p">,</span>
                     <span class="n">print_to_console</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="kc">False</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">num_levels</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="n">grid_level</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">seed</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="n">seed</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">num_resamples</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="mi">100</span><span class="p">)</span>

    <span class="n">Si2</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">ee_analyze</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">problem_info</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">parameter_values</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">qoi_sensitivity_outputs2</span><span class="p">[:,</span> <span class="n">experimental_point</span><span class="p">],</span> <span class="n">conf_level</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="mf">0.95</span><span class="p">,</span>
                     <span class="n">print_to_console</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="kc">False</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">num_levels</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="n">grid_level</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">seed</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="n">seed</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">num_resamples</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="mi">100</span><span class="p">)</span>

    <span class="n">Si3</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">ee_analyze</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">problem_info</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">parameter_values</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">qoi_sensitivity_outputs3</span><span class="p">[:,</span> <span class="n">experimental_point</span><span class="p">],</span> <span class="n">conf_level</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="mf">0.95</span><span class="p">,</span>
                     <span class="n">print_to_console</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="kc">False</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">num_levels</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="n">grid_level</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">seed</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="n">seed</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">num_resamples</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="mi">100</span><span class="p">)</span>
